promptcontent: Please rate how good this sentence sounds to you using the scale below, with 1 being very bad and 7 being very good.

instructions.instructions-0:
In this experiment, you will hear a sentence and then be asked to rate how good it sounds to you.

Because you will only hear each sentence once, please make sure to be in a quiet room, and headphones are strongly encouraged.
instructions.instructions-1:

At the end, we will ask you a few questions about your language background. Please return to the original Qualtrics window to complete these language background questions once you are finished.

This experiment has been reviewed and given the status EXEMPT by the University of Michigan IRB [HUM00142209]. Please contact the PI (savithry@umich.edu) if you have any questions or concerns.

exit.exit-0:
Thank you! Your responses have been recorded.

Please return to the original Qualtrics survey window to complete a few questions about your language background. You are free to close this window.
